Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.80,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:31.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Let's get out of here. When I count to five, run left.
