Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.92,0:00:33.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,four,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.93,0:00:34.97,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,three,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.97,0:00:35.93,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,two,
