Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.48,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,Aw, come on! Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:45.81,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Darn.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:49.23,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,The girls were supposed to be chasing after us...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:51.78,Default,Yamaoka,0,0,0,,Look at 'em. They're just like the Beatles!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.24,0:00:54.11,Default,Seiji,0,0,0,,They've taught me something valuable.
