Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:38.17,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Pops!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.17,0:02:39.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I know it's been a while...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:42.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:43.64,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.18,0:02:45.72,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen... What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:52.23,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Richie, can you check to see if Brother Jun's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.61,0:02:54.11,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.11,0:02:57.07,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Summer vacation's over, so why would Jun be—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.07,0:02:57.61,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.86,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,a lot's happened while you boys weren't around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:04.16,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He's not here now though. Left last week.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.08,0:03:05.74,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Either way,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.29,0:03:08.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,it sure has been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.75,0:03:09.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.58,0:03:12.38,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I've been waiting for you, Richie-rich.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.09,0:03:16.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,My piano trio is finally together again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.26,0:03:24.14,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Junichi was disowned by his father right after he came back this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.60,0:03:25.93,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Disowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.93,0:03:29.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Well, first he went against his parents' wishes by going to college in Tokyo,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:32.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,then stopped going to school.{this and previous needs serious retiming}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:35.02,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Instead, he got wrapped up in some political activism.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.48,0:03:38.57,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,So, when the prodigal son wandered back on home,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.57,0:03:41.28,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,his father was understandably furious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.74,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Junichi wasn't allowed to set foot in his own house...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.74,0:03:47.20,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,And not long after, I ran into him at the bar,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.84,0:03:49.75,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,blitzed out of his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.96,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,so I let him take refuge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.92,0:03:53.71,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Pops...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.21,0:03:58.05,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Is it my fault that Brother Jun left?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.05,0:04:00.09,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Oh, no. That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.09,0:04:02.47,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,He happened to find a cheap place for rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.64,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:06.26,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.56,0:04:12.89,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sentaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.90,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Don't just mope your life away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.49,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,One good session'll drive those blues away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.24,0:04:24.53,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,N-Never mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.20,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Pretend that never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.04,0:04:31.62,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I get it, Mr. Bill Evans, I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:33.37,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.37,0:04:35.88,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What d'you say we play some to stop me from moping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.51,0:04:46.59,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Junichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:50.97,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.56,0:04:56.56,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.81,0:04:58.98,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Don't ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.32,0:05:10.91,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}What made him change this much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:17.29,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1\t(4074,5075,\c&HF7F7F7&\3c&HF7F7F7&)}That day last winter, in the basement... What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:21.25,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he just do it on a whim?{Probably just wanted to molest high school girls}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:38.69,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if I knock,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:41.19,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}he might not open the door...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:50.95,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or would he just look at me again with those vacant eyes?{The cold, dead eyes of a drug fiend}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.17,0:06:00.63,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry, but that doesn't suit you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.26,0:06:07.34,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.09,0:06:10.47,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,That angry face of yours just kills me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.26,0:06:14.52,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You had that same expression when we first met, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.52,0:06:15.89,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I remember it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.69,0:06:21.98,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.44,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Just go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:24.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Or...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.58,0:06:40.92,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,Hey, Mukae!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.25,0:06:43.21,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.96,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,Could you give this to Nishimi for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.01,0:06:50.43,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Um, wouldn't it be better if you gave it to him yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.01,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,Oh, no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.01,0:06:53.68,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,I'd be too nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.93,Default,Girl A,0,0,0,,So, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.14,0:06:56.81,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Nice work!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.23,0:07:00.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:03.98,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's been a while since the festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:05.69,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,but you're as popular as ever, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:07.82,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.12,0:07:25.17,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I staring at?{His firm buttocks}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:26.67,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}What, am I jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.67,0:07:28.55,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has nothing to do with me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:30.13,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Ritsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.59,0:07:34.14,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Hey, which scarf design do you like better?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.05,0:07:38.72,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Actually, y'see, there's this guy I kinda like
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:41.39,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,and I'm thinkin' about making one for him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.39,0:07:42.35,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Who? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:44.15,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,I can't say yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:46.44,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,But how about you, Ritsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.44,0:07:48.53,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Is there anybody that you'd wanna knit for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:51.49,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Come on, let's knit together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:56.08,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,But I don't have anyone to give it to...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.08,0:07:57.24,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Oh, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:07:59.45,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Be honest with yourself, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.45,0:08:02.62,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,You were totally staring at a certain someone just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:05.21,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,It's not what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:06.09,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Don't get the wrong idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:07.75,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:10.88,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Nishimi is just a friend, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:13.51,Default,Tokie,0,0,0,,Sorry! Just a sec!{She likes them fat train otaku}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.85,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a nice color...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.94,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I bet Kaoru would look good in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:28.65,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:31.69,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's wrong with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.41,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why is my heart beating so fast?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.99,0:08:39.41,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,That day in the basement?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:40.70,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.75,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I almost forgot about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.17,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You wanna know why I did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.17,0:08:50.17,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Was it a little bit too much for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.22,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry. I was just feeling kinda mischievous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:08:59.43,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.85,0:09:02.14,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.14,0:09:04.19,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Didn't you come in because you wanted this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.60,0:09:06.40,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What were you hoping for?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.44,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,A declaration of love?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.90,0:09:11.36,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint you, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:13.53,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,But this is the kind of guy I am. {A paedophile}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.78,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You stopped fighting back...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.78,0:09:21.58,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You just gonna take it after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.12,0:09:22.91,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:27.08,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,"If I act like this, she'll probably take off."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.92,0:09:29.08,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,Is that what you're thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:33.96,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.59,0:09:36.34,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,You can do what you want with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:41.18,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.52,0:09:43.64,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.94,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,and don't ever come back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:48.98,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I'm not the same person I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:53.11,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I dropped out of college and got disowned by my own flesh and blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:58.07,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Society gave me the boot, so it's all over for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.78,0:10:02.08,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Just being close to me will ruin your life, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.79,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,If you know what I'm sayin', just get the hell out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:18.72,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.30,0:10:22.22,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,I'm sick of being called a young lady.{will need to be retimed probably}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.64,0:10:25.47,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,So I'll just remove everything that makes me one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:29.48,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,If you're not the same person you once were,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:34.40,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,then I can become someone else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:38.28,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,150)}Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.90,0:10:42.49,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1\fad(0,250)}I'm gonna become someone else, a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:44.03,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:52.29,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Don't go wasting something so precious for a loser like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.43,0:11:05.14,Default,Arita,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you're the Katsuragi I've heard so much about...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.93,0:11:08.89,Default,Arita,0,0,0,,{\i1}How about a few words to mark the occasion?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.27,0:11:10.02,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.27,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I'm just passing through,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:18.40,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'd like to talk to you about what a college {\i0}should{\i1} be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:20.78,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:23.03,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're my inspiration.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.03,0:11:31.08,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1.5\fs40\c&H5A6661&\b1\pos(829,551)}Every {\c&H202625&}Rebel {\c&H131613&}has a {\c&H0E1110&}Cause
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.33,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Muroi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.33,0:11:28.34,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listening to your speech
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:32.50,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}made me feel so down on myself for doing nothing but studying and playing music.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:33.00,signs,,0,0,0,,{\fax0.1\blur1.2\fs33\c&HF9FFFA&\frz337.2\org(1052,286)\b1\pos(776,392)\frx334\fry344}The Decline of a False System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.50,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fax0.05\blur1.2\fs33\c&HD1D3CF&\frz349.6\frx352\fry356\org(725,490)\pos(393,640)}The Decline of a False System
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:42.51,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fax-0.03\blur1.1\fs20\c&H2D2D33&\b0\frz9.922\frx358\fry0\org(934,205)\fnObelixPro\pos(720,271)}Strike Against \NRising Tuition
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.50,0:11:42.51,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fs30\fnObelixPro\c&H0A0B0B&\frz345.5\frx6\fry16\org(97,621)\pos(173,603)}All Students \Non Strike
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.80,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Katsuragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.51,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}in the next battle, if something happens to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.34,0:11:46.89,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}you'd take over for me, right? Even for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.47,0:11:49.85,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Arita, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.19,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fs20\fnCreativeBlock BB\b1\c&H000000&\pos(1065,469)\frz344\frx352\fry356}Japan Communist\N Youth Union
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.15,0:11:55.19,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur1.2\fs20\fnCreativeBlock BB\b1\c&H000000&\frx352\fry356\frz354\pos(917,245)}Japan Communist\N Youth Union
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.23,0:11:57.94,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Muroi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:00.44,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come over once in a while and play sax with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.66,0:12:07.16,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi! Arita's been arrested!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:18.75,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}The bones are shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.59,0:12:22.26,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}so the doc told me my fingers won't be able to move like they used to.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.51,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}B-But the sax...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.51,0:12:25.76,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't play anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.35,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't look so glum, Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:33.39,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I can dump everything I don't need and just focus on the movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:37.36,Default,Muroi,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm gonna become someone else, a new me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.53,0:12:46.12,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:48.16,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Katsuragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.58,0:12:49.95,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey... Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:51.08,Default,Guy,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.46,0:13:04.68,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,I don't wanna see any more people get hurt because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:11.35,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,I don't know what happened to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:12.81,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,You don't have to talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.89,0:13:18.19,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,But I can see that you're hurt deeply.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.02,0:13:23.28,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Why don't you let me support you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:27.53,Default,Yukari,0,0,0,,Am I being too pushy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:33.66,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.91,0:13:37.71,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,You're a pushy woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.06,0:13:56.52,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Maybe I better stop takin' naps on the roof...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.61,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Hey, wasn't that Yurika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:01.98,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Did the teacher call her aside again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.90,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.03,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,Yurika's been acting so weird lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:07.32,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,She's totally changed...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.32,0:14:10.12,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,It seems like her innocence is completely gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:12.12,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Maybe something happened to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:15.12,Default,Girl 2,0,0,0,,I asked her that, but she wouldn't answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:17.87,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,Well, since she cut her hair like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:19.21,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.50,0:14:20.58,Default,Girl 1,0,0,0,,A broken heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.96,0:14:24.59,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.38,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}What'd he do to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.84,0:14:29.84,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}So you're Sentaro, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.34,0:14:31.85,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do you like jazz?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.39,0:14:38.35,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ever since I first met Brother Jun, he's been like a big brother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wanted to get good at jazz like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.73,0:14:43.02,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be strong like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.86,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Be cool like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.95,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I tried to follow in his footsteps, every step of the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:51.70,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}thinking I'd eventually catch up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:52.95,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Sen-boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:56.75,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your woman forgot something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.25,0:15:05.96,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}If he'd just sit down and talk to me, maybe I'd understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.42,0:15:11.22,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if he did something to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.93,0:15:12.68,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.10,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,B-Brother Jun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:23.69,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I need to talk to—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.20,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Son of a bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:35.16,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.16,0:15:38.91,Default,Jun,0,0,0,,He's the one person I didn't want to find out about this.{That I'm fucking a high school girl}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:41.29,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,But what else could you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.92,0:15:44.50,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,He was bound to find out sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:51.30,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:54.80,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew she was out of my league from the start...{More like you were playing the wrong sport}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:57.51,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.51,0:15:58.77,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or I thought I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:13.99,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just can't figure it out...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.62,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know for sure that when I'm with Kaoru,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.62,0:16:21.20,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I feel completely at ease and I have a good time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:23.96,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:26.54,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I decided a long time ago who I should like.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:29.96,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey, Ritsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:32.97,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Is Sen around?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:35.84,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:39.39,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Knitting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.89,0:16:41.85,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why would she bother hiding that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.31,0:16:48.02,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:01.87,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.62,0:17:03.00,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.00,0:17:07.04,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:08.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:12.80,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,What d'you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:15.76,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You're obviously acting strangely today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.34,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Tell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:19.81,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,I saw 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.18,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Saw who?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:23.60,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,When I went to Brother Jun's apartment...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.10,0:17:25.06,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,She was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.69,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Y-You're sure you saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.69,0:17:30.19,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.77,0:17:34.49,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,And of all people, it had to be Brother Jun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.49,0:17:36.11,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,That's what hurts the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.07,0:17:39.87,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,Anyway, it's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.87,0:17:41.24,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,There's nothin' I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:45.75,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,You've still got it good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.50,0:17:50.38,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Even though you were rejected, you've still got someone who cares for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.84,0:17:52.50,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Can't see the forest for the trees, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.51,0:17:58.68,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,And those trees are so tall, you obviously can't see a damn thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.26,0:18:02.47,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Why don't you try opening your eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.47,0:18:04.93,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Isn't it about high time you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.56,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,W-What're you talkin' about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.56,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Figure it out for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:16.57,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.57,0:18:17.65,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Kaoru?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.99,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,You just got here and you're leaving already?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Yeah. I've got some things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.37,0:18:25.70,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Are you done knitting for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:28.62,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:30.63,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I couldn't help but glance over before...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.34,0:18:34.46,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,I'm sure he'll really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.01,0:18:37.88,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Aw look, you're blushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.88,0:18:39.34,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Was I right on the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:41.09,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,Well, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.43,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Wait a min—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:51.48,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure this is for the best...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.94,0:18:55.94,Default,Kaoru,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't have a relapse! It shouldn't hurt at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:03.16,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I won't have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.87,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,You and this man from God knows where...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:10.08,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Yurika, you're being deceived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.17,Default,Yurika,0,0,0,,What do you know, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.17,0:19:14.46,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:18.59,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,I'll bring home a suitable partner for you soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.59,0:19:22.68,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,So don't meet with this man again, Yurika.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:23.68,Default,Dad,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:31.77,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Yurika, your father is just being so harsh because he's so worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.27,0:19:38.03,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Girls like us have to take better care of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:42.99,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Just in case, keep next Saturday open, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:45.78,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,I made an appointment for you at the gynecologist.{whoa, what}{Gotta check you're purity...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.17,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fnChristopherhand\frz18.91\c&H040B0E&\pos(476,92)}Are you eating properly?\N Here's a letter that came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:57.17,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.6\fnChristopherhand\frz18.91\c&H040B0E&\pos(461,466)}Love, Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.72,0:20:05.72,signs,Sign,0,0,0,,{\blur0.7\fs60\fnlemon squeezy\b1\c&H000000&\frz342.1\frx354\fry352\pos(654,94)}To my comrade,\N from Isao Arita
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:15.73,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Richie, that rat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:18.48,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Throws out hints, then just leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.78,0:20:21.36,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Someone who cares for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:23.28,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did he mean my family?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.86,Default,Sen,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:32.62,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,So you're gonna be the Virgin Mary in the Christmas play, huh, Sachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.62,0:20:33.46,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.58,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,But I'm really nervous...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:39.38,Default,Ritsuko,0,0,0,,Hashiguchi will be there to see you too, so you have to do your best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.71,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,D-Don't mention him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.71,0:20:41.92,Default,Sachiko,0,0,0,,I don't care if he—{I-It's not like I like him. B-Baka!}
